{"title":"Hexo 网站初始化","date":"2022-04-25T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年4月25日","L":"2022/04/25","MM-DD":"04-25"},"link":"hexo-web-site-init","tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2022-04-24T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<p>第一步</p>\n<p>初始化：<code>hexo init</code></p>\n<p>安装 主题<br>\n使用的主题：<code>inside</code><br>\n地址：<code>https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li>进入博客目录 <code>project/</code> , 执行以下命令：</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-theme-inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>配置：<code>project/_config.yml</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">inside</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>创建主题文件：<code>project/_config.inside.yml</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<!-- https://github.com/omnibingo/talk2.it -->\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"个性化调整:\">个性化调整:<a title=\"#个性化调整:\" href=\"#个性化调整:\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"设置文章头高度:\">设置文章头高度:<a title=\"#设置文章头高度:\" href=\"#设置文章头高度:\"></a></h4>\n<p>CSS文件: <code>styles.91e7dfca63c7c151daa6.css</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fn&#123;padding-top:37%</span><br><span class=\"line\">调整为:</span><br><span class=\"line\">fn&#123;padding-top:24%;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"去掉文章底部上一个下一个按钮\">去掉文章底部上一个下一个按钮<a title=\"#去掉文章底部上一个下一个按钮\" href=\"#去掉文章底部上一个下一个按钮\"></a></h4>\n<p>JS文件: <code>main.543c891b4aad158701f3.js</code><br>\n找到以下代码属性拼接<code>1</code>即可<br>\n可根据关键字:<code>post.prev</code> <code>post.next</code>查找</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">uy</span>(<span class=\"params\">t, e</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"number\">1</span> &amp; t &amp;&amp; (<span class=\"title class_\">So</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;a&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">31</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Bo</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">xo</span>()), <span class=\"number\">2</span> &amp; t) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">const</span> t = <span class=\"title class_\">Do</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t.<span class=\"property\">ngIf</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"title class_\">No</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;routerLink&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;/&quot;</span>, t.<span class=\"property\">post</span>.<span class=\"property\">prev</span>.<span class=\"property\">link1</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Ws</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Wo</span>(t.<span class=\"property\">post</span>.<span class=\"property\">prev</span>.<span class=\"property\">title1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">hy</span>(<span class=\"params\">t, e</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"number\">1</span> &amp; t &amp;&amp; (<span class=\"title class_\">So</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;a&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">32</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Bo</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">xo</span>()), <span class=\"number\">2</span> &amp; t) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">const</span> t = <span class=\"title class_\">Do</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t.<span class=\"property\">ngIf</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"title class_\">No</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;routerLink&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;/&quot;</span>, t.<span class=\"property\">post</span>.<span class=\"property\">next</span>.<span class=\"property\">link1</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Ws</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Wo</span>(t.<span class=\"property\">post</span>.<span class=\"property\">next</span>.<span class=\"property\">title1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">dy</span>(<span class=\"params\">t, e</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"number\">1</span> &amp; t &amp;&amp; (<span class=\"title class_\">So</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;div&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">28</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">_o</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>, uy, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;a&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">29</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">_o</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>, hy, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;a&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">30</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">xo</span>()), <span class=\"number\">2</span> &amp; t) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">const</span> t = <span class=\"title class_\">Do</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t.<span class=\"property\">ngIf</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"title class_\">Ws</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">wo</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;ngIf&quot;</span>, t.<span class=\"property\">post</span>.<span class=\"property\">prev1</span>), <span class=\"title class_\">Ws</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>), <span class=\"title function_\">wo</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;ngIf&quot;</span>, t.<span class=\"property\">post</span>.<span class=\"property\">next1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"引入通用js脚本\">引入通用JS脚本<a title=\"#引入通用js脚本\" href=\"#引入通用js脚本\"></a></h4>\n<p>主题文件夹下找到: <code>layout</code> 文件夹下的 <code>index.njk</code> 文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight diff\"><figcaption><span>index.njk</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!doctype html&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;html lang=&quot;&#123;&#123; config.language &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;title&gt;&#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;base href=&quot;&#123;&#123; config.root &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=0&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=&quot;canonical&quot; href=&quot;&#123;&#123; url_trim(url) &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=&quot;icon&quot; type=&quot;image/x-icon&quot; href=&quot;&#123;&#123; url_for(theme.favicon) &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"addition\">+ &lt;!--引入JS--&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"addition\">+ &lt;script src=&quot;https://libs.baidu.com/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"addition\">+ &lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.bootcdn.net/ajax/libs/echarts/4.9.0-rc.1/echarts-en.common.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% if theme.pwa.manifest -%&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=&quot;manifest&quot; href=&quot;&#123;&#123; url_for(&#x27;manifest.json&#x27;) &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-mobile-web-app-capable&quot; content=&quot;yes&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;meta name=&quot;apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style&quot; content=&quot;black-translucent&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;&#123; open_graph(&#123; image: page.thumbnail if page.thumbnail else theme.profile.avatar &#125;) &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;&#123; structured_data(page) if theme.seo.structured_data -&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% if config.feed and config.feed.path -%&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;application/atom+xml&quot; title=&quot;&#123;&#123; config.title &#125;&#125;&quot; href=&quot;&#123;&#123; url_for(config.feed.path) &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;&#123; ga(theme.ga) if theme.ga &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;body lang=&quot;&#123;&#123; config.language &#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"修改页面底部文案\">修改页面底部文案<a title=\"#修改页面底部文案\" href=\"#修改页面底部文案\"></a></h4>\n<p>主题文件夹下找到: <code>lib</code> 文件夹下的 <code>config.js</code> 文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight diff